Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:05.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,作为游戏界前途无量的新人程序员活跃在一线的木户
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:07.22,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,1992年10月 《超级马里奥赛车》（任天堂）发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:10.82,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,1991年《刺猬索尼克》（世嘉）发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:14.09,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,1991年《塞尔达传说 众神的三角之力》（任天堂）发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:18.00,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,1991年《最终幻想4》（史克威尔）发售
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:07.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:11.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,虽然毕业了 却找不到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱着对未来的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,过着混日子的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,又输了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,香织酱好强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:58.97,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,（礼治在玩的游戏是《超真实麻雀P4》）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:01.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:02.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:06.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,（诶？不玩了吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:09.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这叫什么玩意啊 连街霸2都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说起来全是老游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,去别的地方吧  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你也赶紧去找个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:25.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我要卖了这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:49.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一边找工作一边帮家里的事 会不会到头来一头都占不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,一个像素的误差就会招来死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:15.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,特别是这个业界最早出现的横版卷轴射击游戏《宇宙巡航机》系列
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:19.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要打通它必须有特定的攻略模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:23.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,大量玩家在一次次反复的Game over之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:27.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,最终才制作出来的美丽的攻略模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:31.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再现这一攻略 需要精密的操作和精神力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那就再玩一回呗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,漏掉一个密封舱都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那就再玩一回呗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:43.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这种夹杆握法是很怕外界冲击的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨了  放个50圆的镚儿重来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:47.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想要让KID再多用50圆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我说 礼治君 这太差劲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:09.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,紧握着一个50圆的钢镚儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:13.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,跑到机厅的小孩 你难道不明白他们的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:14.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你公司那边很顺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,稍微给我们家的营业额做点贡献怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去这家店就要没了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爹说要把这里卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:34.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也是 这是在家里玩游戏的时代了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:41.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,的确 现在DQ和FF这样的RPG是超有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:46.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明年发售的SEGA Saturn和Play Station的街机游戏移植大概也很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:51.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 或许去机厅玩游戏就完全失去了意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,别这么一本正经地接话茬好不 还不一定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:57.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道 总有一天机厅的时代会再次到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:04:59.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 绝对会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天是哪天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这你是不当自家事 完全不负责任的说法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我们家可没这样的余地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:10.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 礼治君你这不是也当真了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老子不打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:38.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户君 可以不关呼机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:43.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,又下单子了 得马上做个新的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,杂志的采访 今天也有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？木户君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:58.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在木户君是业界的领跑者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你不要再出入这种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我回公司了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:22.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 公司接了那么多单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治君你其实也认真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不肯承认呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么好主意啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户在游戏界是相当有名的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托木户……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我说你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道KID在这圈子里很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:01.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这种活跃在最前端的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:05.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在会对这种落魄机厅上心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,当然会上心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:10.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,知道这里要没 会马上来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不 我会让他来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,听好 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:18.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,出人头地的男人 都是冷酷的 无情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:23.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为了追寻理想 可以毫不留情的舍弃旧日的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,作为男人 也需要有这种坚定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你要也算是KID的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就别做拖他后腿的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:38.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,太搞笑了 听不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:44.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,拖老婆后腿的又是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过别来这边儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你欠债的事情都有电话打到我公司了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 你是保证人赶紧想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哇 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你这绊脚的羁绊 我也想赶紧扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:02.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这点还请您睁只眼闭只眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不来妈妈的公司工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,诶？公司？是说花店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 妈妈说这个很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,突然说这个干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:23.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你爸提出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:28.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,别这么盯着我看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:39.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 老妈 最近老爸很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,突然说什么要把店卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,之前经营上一直都很困难但是这次突然就说卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,最近也突然开始念我找工作找工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:50.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想让你赶紧安定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,想让儿子过上不输别人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,父母都会这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 别当着我的面说我的闲话好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说起来店到底怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还是要关张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:07.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没错 店要关张 卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:13.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,呐 礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这家店 会这样一直慢慢垮掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你想看到？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户说过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:29.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,机厅的时代还会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,骗人了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么骗人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:01.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,要不是骗了人你怎么能找到什么正经工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:03.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,就你这样的败家子儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:18.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 礼治 回太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,怀旧的老游戏机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 也有这样的卖点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是我们家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,跟高野同学说明了情况之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧和认识的写手进行了沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,让这个企划通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:54.50,注释,,0000,0000,0000,,（回顾过去 新锐游戏制作人 畅谈游戏机厅的魅力）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:11:00.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,介绍有意思的东西才是杂志嘛 理所当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:06.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这里对我们来说是很重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,坐立不安的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 继续努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:26.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 能不能别把这家店卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 已经晚了 早就找到买家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:35.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,买卖手续也开始办了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:40.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也没有精力再经营这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那让我来经营吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我要做这里的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:06.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,今后机厅的形势会越来越严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:09.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这里的经营 也会比现在……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:11.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:17.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在家用游戏的势头确实很猛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:21.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这也表示游戏界全体非常火热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:25.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,而且 机厅有机厅的好处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:31.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,个体独立的操作性 洗练的画面 具有临场感的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:36.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,还有 喜欢游戏的人们聚集起来的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:39.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,玩家们一定会发现这里的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:46.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,机厅渡边在不远的将来一定会复活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,木户
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我也会协助礼治君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:14:00.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:06.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,用50圆打通 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,Fantasy Zone？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:16.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,做到的话 就把这家店给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:28.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,OK 那 完事了叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这里就用夹杆握法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 硬币全都要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,可以买到强化道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,主角Opaopa为了拯救全银河的货币危机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,在8个星球上进行冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:21.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒各个星球上所有前线基地 BOSS就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:27.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,货位危机…… 还真是很费心思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这个巨大的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个游戏的最终BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,主人公Opaopa的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:52.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的力量超越被外星人操纵的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:56.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这是Opaopa身上的最终试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是么 一定要打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:14.14,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你是在继承这家机厅的星辰下诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:17.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,谁会继承这种破机厅 机厅简直像屎一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你终于也明白游戏的好处了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:20.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,店怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:24.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,做到的话 就把这家店给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,最近老爸很怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:41.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:47.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:48.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,哪里疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:49.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,胸口？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,内脏 内脏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:52.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,内脏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:54.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这个人也会病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:17.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,人干不过岁数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:28.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你爸啊 替我呆在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,跟你还有你的朋友们一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:42.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,除了这个什么都干不了 完全干不了工作的一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:56.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 只会工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,运动会不是还来过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是去过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有那么一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸做的便当真是很难吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是挺香的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:35.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真不吉利 跟人死了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:40.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸之前也没做过一件对身体好的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这样之后也会注意点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 关于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,啊 下定决心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我是决定真心想开机厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,买卖可不是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:13.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有干一辈子的自信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不会麻烦妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:24.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那就加油做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:43.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,为什么老爸要去花店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,疗养 住院 有时花店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:47.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈突然打电话说有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔露个面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,好开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:13.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,你是第二代？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:17.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那么前代欠的钱也是第二代继承
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,现在大概到600万了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,这站着说话也不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,也想顺便确认一下里面的财产情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:36.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:37.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.80,0:21:54.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,倒闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:10.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,喂 木户君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:13.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我现在到渡边了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想让你查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:19.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我现在把照片传给你
